projectInfo.name: Economic Development - Ambanja (Diégo Suarez), Madagascar
projectInfo.shortDescription: The city of Ambaja has no effective map showing points of interests and tourist circuits, but still Antsiranana and its region can prevail themselves of  grandiose landscapes and a very rich history. This mapping project will allow to **make this cultural and natural heritage more visible for tourists, bringing the voice of their communities**, and it will favor the economic development of the region.
projectInfo.description:
- Requesting organization : **OSM MG / Antsiranana community**
- Authors  : **CartONG / OSM MG**
- Difficulty : **Easy**
- Imagery : **Bing**

This projects aims to mapping the city of Ambaja, in the north of Madagascar.

Why? The city of Ambaja has no effective map showing points of interests and tourist circuits, but still Ambaja and its region can prevail themselves of  grandiose landscapes and a very rich history. This mapping project will allow to **make this cultural and natural heritage more visible for tourists, bringing the voice of their communities**, and it will favor the economic development of the region. This remote mapping will be followed by the local community. Once the necessary data are collected, the local community will be able to spread its touristic map of the city!
